# Disclaimer

This project is an educational proof-of-concept built using synthetic banking data.

It does not use confidential customer information, proprietary banking systems, or production transaction logs.

The analytical workflow, modeling strategy, and validation framework are intended to demonstrate industry-relevant approaches to banking operations analytics and model validation.

